	<section>
		<h1>Sources & Licenses</h1>
		<p>
			Lumen only includes materials that are legal to share, 
			preserve, and study without commercial intent.
		</p>

		<h2>Allowed Licenses</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Public Domain</strong></li>
			<li><strong>CC0</strong> (Creative Commons Zero)</li>
			<li><strong>Creative Commons</strong> (CC-BY, CC-BY-SA, CC-BY-NC)</li>
			<li><strong>Official Educational Releases</strong> with explicit sharing permission</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Trusted Sources</h2>
		<ul class="video-list">
			<li class="video-item">
				<span class="title">NASA Image and Video Library</span>
				<span class="meta">Public domain imagery and video from the United States space agency.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="video-item">
				<span class="title">ESA Multimedia</span>
				<span class="meta">Educational and public domain content from the European Space Agency.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="video-item">
				<span class="title">Internet Archive</span>
				<span class="meta">Non-profit library of millions of free books, movies, and more.</span>
			</li>
			<li class="video-item">
				<span class="title">The Prelinger Archives</span>
				<span class="meta">Ephemeral films documenting historical life and industry.</span>
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 style="color: var(--accent-color);">What is not allowed</h2>
		<p>To protect the integrity of the library and its viewers, the following are strictly prohibited:</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>YouTube reuploads</strong> without verifiable original ownership.</li>
			<li><strong>Clips without original context</strong> or fragmented edits.</li>
			<li><strong>Commercial films or series</strong>.</li>
			<li><strong>Content with unclear or restrictive licenses</strong>.</li>
		</ul>

		<div style="margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted-text); padding: 1.5rem; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-left: 2px solid var(--border-color);">
			<p>
				<strong>Decision Policy:</strong> If a source cannot be verified, it is not included. Assumption is treated as failure.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you believe any content on Lumen violates your copyright, please contact us for immediate removal.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
